* "Talons (XXXChange Remix)" <U+2013> 6:30 <U+2013> track 17 on the deluxe North American edition
* "Talons" (Acoustic) <U+2013> 4:32 <U+2013> track 15 on the iTunes version
* "Signs" (Acoustic) <U+2013> 3:24 <U+2013> track 16 on the iTunes version

=== Vinyl ===
* A standard black LP copy in a [[gatefold]] sleeve was released in October 2008 with the normal track listing, but with an original mix of "Mercury" instead of the CD version.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://eil.com/shop/moreinfo.asp?catalogid=451127|title=Intimacy UK LP|publisher=Esprit International|accessdate=17 July 2009 }}</ref> The North American edition also included a code for the free online download of the tracks in MP3 format.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://eil.com/shop/moreinfo.asp?catalogid=456455|title=Intimacy USA LP Record|publisher=Esprit International|accessdate=17 July 2009 }}</ref>
* A limited edition picture disc vinyl version was additionally released in the UK; it had the album cover printed on Side A and the track listing printed on Side B.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://eil.com/shop/moreinfo.asp?catalogid=451128|title=Intimacy UK LP Picture Disc|publisher=Esprit International|accessdate=17 July 2009 }}</ref>

